collection.description:
**NFT HUD Founders Lifetime Access Membership**

The Best NFT Tools all on one platform.

**Join the NFT HUD Founders Membership for:**

- [x] Unlimited access to [nfthud.io](https://nfthud.io/)
- [x] Exclusive access to the Founders Club [Discord](https://discord.gg/nfthud)
- [x] WL access to other NFT projects (Owning multiple NFTs gets more WL chances)

**Holding a Founders NFT grants you full access to everything [nfthud.io](https://nfthud.io/) has to offer.**

- [x] High Speed Rarity Rankings *(usually < 2 minutes after mint/reveal)*
- [x] Deal Sniper *(quickly identify insane deals)*
- [x] Trending Tab *(mission control for hot NFTs)*
- [x] NFT Calendar *(easily find the hottest mints each month)*
- [x] NFT Analytics *(data is key)*
- [x] Bulk Bidding *(bid on multiple NFTs easily)*

+ dozens of other new tools!
